<div id="review_1085184698" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1085184698" />
    <a title="Normandie Alleman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16018048-normandie-alleman"><img alt="Normandie Alleman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442657712p2/16018048.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1085184698?book_show_action=true">Oct 20, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Normandie Alleman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Normandie Alleman" href="/user/show/16018048-normandie-alleman">Normandie Alleman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780988755000" href="/book/show/17676172-the-sacred-band">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1085184698" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1909407796303627500">A rich tapestry of myth, war, love, and honor woven with great care by two outstanding authors. This epic book is reminiscent of classic literature and I&apos;d recommend it highly to lovers of such.</span>
  <span id="freeText1909407796303627500" style="display:none">A rich tapestry of myth, war, love, and honor woven with great care by two outstanding authors. This epic book is reminiscent of classic literature and I'd recommend it highly to lovers of such.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1909407796303627500" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

