        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1084181615" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17499323988038635880">THE SACRED BAND is one of the most captivating books of this genre that I have ever read. It is nicely balanced and doesn’t become bogged down in any one aspect of its ancient setting. The gods, demi-gods, and men are portrayed in a splendid, multifaceted, and intense epic worth the read.</span>

